  "description": "When you take damage, you can take a Reaction to give yourself Resistance to that damage and any other damage of the same type until the end of the current turn.\n\nFoundry Note\n\nThis feature includes an Active Effect for resisting each type of damage which can be applied to get the relevant resistance. Be sure you disable/delete the previous Active Effect in the \"Effects\" tab of your sheet when you change Resistances.",
